<s> Anyone know if it would be possible to remap colors on a page using CSS in order to compensate for a specific type of color blindness?  </s>
<s> Could I write a user stylesheet that would take a page where color was used to encode information and remap those colors to something a person with deuteranope could see, for example?  </s>
