<s> It's possible, assuming that we're only talking about CSS.  </s>
<s> I'd imagine you'd want something like this: (1) Download the web page and CSS page.  </s>
<s> Analyze it for color use.  </s>
<s> (2) Set up an appropriate color mapping for the specific type of color blindness.  </s>
<s> (3) Apply that to the page and present to the user.  </s>
<s> Step (3) is pretty easy.  </s>
<s> Step (1) is not so hard.  </s>
<s> Step (2) I'm not sure how hard it is, but it may be relatively easy to do.  </s>
<s> Unfortunately can't do it just by doing, e.g.: (x) Apply a generic style sheet to a page.  </s>
<s> You need to have that analysis and mapping and application  </s>
